asy-parlament-mezhilisindegi-frakciya-basshylarymen-kezdesti;/kz/events/akorda_news/meetings_and_receptions/elbasy-parlament-mezhilisindegi-frakciya-basshylarymen-kezdesti;/kz/events/international_community/telegrammes_and_letters/memleket-basshysynyn-atyna-onyn-kazakstan-respublikasy-prezidenti-bolyp-sailanuyna-bailanysty-gruziya-prezidenti-georgii-margvelashviliden-kuttyktau-zhedelhaty-kelip-tusti;/kz/events/international_community/telegrammes_and_letters/memleket-basshysynyn-atyna-onyn-kazakstan-respublikasy-prezidenti-bolyp-sailanuyna-bailanysty-gruziya-prezidenti-georgii-margvelashviliden-kuttyktau-zhedelhaty-kelip-tusti;/kz/events/international_community/telegrammes_and_letters/memleket-basshysynyn-atyna-onyn-kazakstan-respublikasy-prezidenti-bolyp-sailanuyna-bailanysty-ukraina-prezidenti-petr-poroshenkodan-kuttyktau-zhedelhaty-kelip-tusti;/kz/events/international_community/telegrammes_and_letters/memleket-basshysynyn-atyna-onyn-kazakstan-respublikasy-prezidenti-bolyp-sailanuyna-bailanysty-ukraina-prezidenti-petr-poroshenkodan-kuttyktau-zhedelhaty-kelip-tusti;/kz/events/international_community/foreign_visits/nursultan-nazarbaev-resei-federaciyasy-men-belarus-respublikasynyn-prezidentterimen-kezdesti;/kz/events/international_community/foreign_visits/nursultan-nazarbaev-resei-federaciyasy-men-belarus-respublikasynyn-prezidentterimen-kezdesti;/kz/events/international_community/foreign_visits/elbasy-keden-odagy-elderi-koshbasshylarynyn-ukraina-zhene-europalyk-odak-okilderinin-kezdesuine-katysty;/kz/events/international_community/foreign_visits/elbasy-keden-odagy-elderi-koshbasshylarynyn-ukraina-zhene-europalyk-odak-okilderinin-kezdesuine-katysty;/kz/events/international_community/foreign_visits/nursultan-nazarbaev-ukraina-prezidenti-petr-poroshenkomen-kezdesti;/kz/events/international_community/foreign_visits/nursultan-nazarbaev-ukraina-prezidenti-petr-poroshenkomen-kezdesti;/kz/events/international_community/foreign_visits/memleket-basshysy-nursultan-nazarbaevtyn
